name: Logitech Z200 Multimedia Speakers | Dell USA
description: 10 Watts Peak/5 Watts RMS power produces room-filling sound. Each speaker has one active/powered driver that delivers full range audio and one passive radiator that provides bass extension. Adjust bass level with the tone control dial and customize your listening experience. Simple controls allow you to access power, volume, bass, headphone jack and auxiliary jack on the right speaker.
